            {
              "type": "heading2",
              "content": {
                "text": "What is Empathy Deck?",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Empathy Deck is an art commission for Wellcome Collection by Erica Scourti, part of our exhibition ‘Bedlam: the asylum and beyond’.",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 100,
                    "end": 129,
                    "type": "hyperlink",
                    "data": {
                      "link_type": "Web",
                      "url": "https://wellcomecollection.org/bedlam"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "It is a Twitter bot which generates responses to tweets by its followers. It makes new ‘cards’ from an imaginary, infinite deck of possible responses, composed of images and text generated from Erica’s personal diary and various self help and therapeutic texts. Cards are a gift for the recipient at that moment in time. Empathy Deck also occasionally makes cards for itself.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Empathy Deck is not intended to provide genuine therapy or advice. If you, or somebody you know, would like mental health advice or support you can contact the following resources:",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 0,
                    "end": 65,
                    "type": "strong",
                    "data": {}
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Samaritans 116 123 jo@samaritans.org",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 0,
                    "end": 10,
                    "type": "hyperlink",
                    "data": {
                      "link_type": "Web",
                      "url": "http://Samaritans.org"
                    }
                  },
                  {
